title: Xception, InceptionV3 Ensemble methods
description: IntroWith some experimentation I found that VGG16 and VGG19 did not perform as well as Inception and XceptionV3 on the data. Therefore this kernel is about how to get the best out of the Xception and InceptionV3 pretrained weights using different ensembling methods.
